<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans II. von Degenberg, Viztum von Amberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache bei Heinrich Nothafft zur Freilassung eines Gefangenen, damit im Gegenzug der unschuldige Konrad Weißenburger, Bürger zu Nürnberg, freikommt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_80" id="38v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_80_r1l14"> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen Gewolff 
<del rend="strikethrough">vicʒtum </del> vom Degenberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l15">vıcʒtum cʒu Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_80_r1l16">Lıeber her vicʒtum / Als Conrad weiſſenburger <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_line_1574357598423_52">
<add><ab facs="#facs_80_line_1576658636215_4995">Beheim gefangen </ab><ab facs="#facs_80_line_1576658639394_5000">iſt worden </ab></add> von eins wegen / den her <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft gefangen hat / als das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l19">der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ſelber auch wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l20">wirdt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l21"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> gen dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft fürderlıch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l22">beholffen ſein wöllet / Ob 
<del rend="strikethrough">Er den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_80_line_1574357700012_67">der </ab></add> ~ den Er gefangen hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l23">ledig werden möht / den vvorten / daʒ der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_80_r1l24">Burger auch ledig würde / Das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_80" id="38v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen Gewolff vom Degenberg, vicztum czu
                        Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vicztum, als Conrad Weissenburger, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, czu <add>Beheim gefangen ist worden</add>
                        von eins wegen, den her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft gefangen
                        hat, als das der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> selber auch wol
                            <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wirdt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, gen dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft fürderlich und beholffen sein
                        wöllet, ob <add>der</add>, den er gefangen hat, ledig werden möht, den
                        worten, daz der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, auch ledig würde. Das wöllen
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
